<h2 class="bold font-l">Kill la Kill</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Satsuki Kiryuin backstabs Ragyo, her mother, revealing that Honnouji Academy was always made to stop Ragyo's plans of conquest. </p>
